penguins: Palmer Penguins

Source: R/penguins.R
penguins.Rd

The Palmer Penguins dataset contains penguins measurements.

Usage

penguins

Format

A data frame with 344 rows and 9 variables:

rowid

Unique identifier assigned to each penguin observation. (Range: 1 to 344)

species

Categorical classification of the penguin species. (Examples: Adelie, Gentoo, Chinstrap)

island

Sampling location of the penguin observation. (Examples: Torgersen, Biscoe, Dream)

bill_length_mm

Length of the penguin's bill measured in millimeters. (Range: 32.1 to 59.6)

bill_depth_mm

Depth of the penguin's bill measured in millimeters. (Range: 13.1 to 21.5)

flipper_length_mm

Length of the penguin's flipper measured in millimeters. (Range: 172 to 231)

body_mass_g

Body mass of the penguin measured in grams. (Range: 2700 to 6300)

sex

Biological sex of the penguin. (Examples: male, female, NA)

year

Year when the penguin observation was recorded. (Examples: 2007, 2008, 2009)
